<subSubSection pageId="157" pageNumber="158" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="157.[264,1323,1368,1554]" pageId="157" pageNumber="158">
During and after the publication of the Parts I and II of the catalogue (
<bibRefCitation author="Monne, M. A." box="[1144,1318,1368,1394]" pageId="157" pageNumber="158" pagination="1 - 765" refId="ref155176" refString="Monne, M. A. (2005 a) Catalogue of the Cerambycidae (Coleoptera) of the Neotropical Region. Part I. Subfamily Cerambycinae. Zootaxa, 946, 1 - 765." type="journal article" year="2005">
Monné, 2005 
<bibRefCitation author="Julio, C. E. A. &amp; Monne, M. A." box="[1305,1318,1368,1394]" pageId="157" pageNumber="158" pagination="446 - 447" refId="ref145774" refString="Julio, C. E. A. &amp; Monne, M. A. (2005 b) Novo genero de Acanthoderini (Coleoptera, Cerambycidae). Revista Brasileira de Entomologia, 49 (4), 446 - 447." type="journal article" year="2005">a</bibRefCitation>
</bibRefCitation>
, 2005b), several papers were published that deal with nomenclatural changes, proposing new names, transferences, new taxa and synonymies, that we add in the addenda. Also homonymies, synonymies, omissions and transferences are added to complete the information concerning the subfamilies 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[676,846,1528,1554]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="157" pageNumber="158" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Cerambycinae">Cerambycinae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1825" box="[903,1018,1528,1554]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="157" pageNumber="158" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Lamiinae">Lamiinae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
